        ", was in fact in Rome and probably was a witness to the proceedings from her palace near the forum. Seeing herself the target of so much animosity she fled from the palace in fear of her life and proceeded to the camp at Ardea.     Brutus opened a debate on the form of government Rome ought to have, a debate at which many ": null
